# To manage my tasks by tmux

## Split project

### 1. (Optional) Rename session

`<Prefix> + $`

### 2. Open session

- New session
  - Create new shell and automatically switch to tmux.
  - Or `tmux new -s <name>`.
- Existing session
  - `<Prefix> + s`

## Split task

### 1. (Optional) Rename window

`<Prefix> + ,`

### 2. Open window

- New window
  - `<Prefix> + c`
- Existing window
  - `<Prefix> + w`

## Commit the task

### Split pane

`<Prefix> + "`

### Switch pane

`<Prefix> + o`

